REAGENT PACK, 100 TESTS
AxSYM Free PSA Reagent Pack
1.	1 Bottle (8.3mL) Anti-PSA coated Microparticles in TRIS buffer with sucrose.

4.	1 Bottle (25.7mL) Specimen Diluent TRIS buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizers. Preservatives: Sodium Azide and Antimicrobial Agents. (Reagent Bottle 4)

Free PSA Controls (concentration: 0.4, 1.0, 7.0 ng/mL)
